---
title: Pork and Fennel Meatballs
description: These meatballs have a delicious secret in them - fennel seeds! Fennel and tarragon are have a similar taste to black licorice, which is an ideal flavour companion to a simple and rustic tomato sauce. Use as little or as much as you want, depending on how much licorice-y flavour you want!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-and-fennel-meatballs-b730a45c.jpg
